<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="walk-v">walk <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /wɔːk/    美 /wɔːk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>走；步行；散步：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>walk home / to school
步行回家/上学</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The door opened and Joe walked in.
门开了，乔走了进来。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s dangerous to <strong>walk the streets</strong> alone at night.
晚上一个人在大街上走很危险。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My mother used to walk 3 kilometers after supper to lose weight.
我妈妈以前为了减肥，晚饭后常常走3公里。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>遛 (动物)；陪 (某人) 走：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>walk</strong> a <strong>dog</strong>
遛狗</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I will <strong>walk</strong> you <strong>to</strong> the bus stop.
我要陪你走到公交车站。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="walk-up-to">walk up (to)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>走近</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="walk-out-on-sb">walk out (on sb)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>遗弃 / 舍弃（某人）</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="walk-out-on-sth">walk out (on sth)</h3>
<p>1.****  </p></div>